"If you find a bug, please do not\n"
"hesitate to send in a bug report.\n"
"We hope you enjoy the software.\n"
"\n"
"The Rasterman - raster@rasterman.com\n"
"Mandrake - mandrake@mandrake.net\n"
"Kim Woelders - kim@woelders.dk\n"
